## ðŸ”¹ How to Run
1. Clone the repository:  
   `git clone https://github.com/ramineqtesad/EECT-EEI-Calculation.git`
2. Install dependencies:  
   `pip install -r requirements.txt`
3. Run the main workflow:  
   `python scripts/run_eei_model.py`
4. Output: Entropy maps, SHAP importance charts, and threshold analysis.

